Labor market cooling https://twitter.com/econberger/status/1632727949605752833

Guy Berger: 1/ @LinkedIn Hiring Rate update:
February was unfortunately a month of bad news: The US LHR was down 6.5% M/M seasonally adjusted, the biggest 1 month decline since 2020.  Hiring is now down 30.8% from April 2022 (when declines began), and 27.9% Y/Y. https://t.co/nMd3IRfPpS
